{"tid":1849842,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企有人重用口罩 我鎖門唔畀佢返會否太絕","createTime":"2020-01-29T09:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T19:34:22.000Z","uid":6097,"like":26,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2be7c67e423fca64786d28768965f3fb1f2715b1","tid":1849842,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:08:41.000Z","msg":"如題 我唔妥佢好撚耐 <br />\n條友將近四十衛生意識極差<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係依兩日先肯帶口罩<br />\n<br />\n據我所知佢係無工開<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但就連續兩日用同一個口罩出去<br />\n<br />\n好撚嘔心 你死你事咪撚搞我<br />\n但怕鎖門好似好絕咁 <br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mgVxr5e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmgVxr5e.png&h=f932ad0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"086a2795be6137562f246c22940e2c14c9705153","tid":1849842,"uid":344729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:10:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6567145366774f18f2dcaee35e4ba55cb62638ba","tid":1849842,"uid":6097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"086a2795be6137562f246c22940e2c14c9705153","tid":1849842,"uid":344729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:10:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:12:24.000Z","msg":"唔係 大佬"},{"pid":"9035f6a2872a642e27d95da51160b92b89dc1d8a","tid":1849842,"uid":3987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:13:15.000Z","msg":"換門鎖啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbcc325f05be60ae71b7e078fa81d843c6e2c0b","tid":1849842,"uid":6097,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"9035f6a2872a642e27d95da51160b92b89dc1d8a","tid":1849842,"uid":3987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:13:15.000Z","msg":"換門鎖啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:21:25.000Z","msg":"真係好嘔心<br />\n同唔帶無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢條仆街賤到仲要到趁我喺廳食飯<br />\n拎個重用口罩喺個廳揚兩下先出門口<br />\n<br />\n好想用火燒將佢連個口罩燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc24c294e4be463d46bad6cdcb2210aee169253","tid":1849842,"uid":233301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:21:35.000Z","msg":"屋企會唔會唔係好夠貨？"},{"pid":"0d41add71f7f039886fa5d33ab3c55bd5739cc73","tid":1849842,"uid":6097,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"0bc24c294e4be463d46bad6cdcb2210aee169253","tid":1849842,"uid":233301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:21:35.000Z","msg":"屋企會唔會唔係好夠貨？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:29:33.000Z","msg":"我哋屋企有三個人<br />\n佢係畀我哋排<br />\n<br />\n我停課到2/17 期間唔打算再出街<br />\n另外一個就一定要返工 口罩得返三十幾個左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重用口罩個廢中根本無工開 所以無可能畀口罩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢就死都要日日出街?????<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945ff8e05bd590ce04163642f19c6a2d54da9569","tid":1849842,"uid":233301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0d41add71f7f039886fa5d33ab3c55bd5739cc73","tid":1849842,"uid":6097,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"0bc24c294e4be463d46bad6cdcb2210aee169253","tid":1849842,"uid":233301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:21:35.000Z","msg":"屋企會唔會唔係好夠貨？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:29:33.000Z","msg":"我哋屋企有三個人<br />\n佢係畀我哋排<br />\n<br />\n我停課到2/17 期間唔打算再出街<br />\n另外一個就一定要返工 口罩得返三十幾個左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重用口罩個廢中根本無工開 所以無可能畀口罩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢就死都要日日出街?????<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:35:15.000Z","msg":"咁過多一個星期應無曬，有無訂緊口罩？<br />\n佢會唔會係出街搵口罩？<br />\n一家人講清楚d好"},{"pid":"1edb580c9a43366d6d57356470ea83d3afac7977","tid":1849842,"uid":53122,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:40:26.000Z","msg":"得番30 個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔重用點夠<br />\n<br />\n你變30 盒出嚟就可以屌佢重用<br />\n<br />\n教佢用微波爐返叮消毒"},{"pid":"79b6e70658309d46d4fd40d89d1dc78846fba2fd","tid":1849842,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:17:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：防毒面具/濾罐 (型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=46a2798f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n個別仔細分析：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護目鏡</span>：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a></span></span> / <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=7c3ad33d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\nVPN 大踢爆：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D112386483628876%26id%3D112357283631796%26__tn__%3D%252As-R&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=84dd6282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家廣傳，避免沉底<br />\n<br />\n最近口罩同N95 都賣曬，部分手足屋企口罩已經就黎用盡，今日同大家介紹下可以防沙士+TG嘅濾罐同濾棉。第一，係for 用曬/買唔到口罩嘅手足，第二係希望方便大家一次過買齊發夢+出街嘅裝備，就算沙士完左，自用送禮都可以繼續名貴大方。<br />\n<br />\nN95/R95/P95 口罩基本上係particulate respirator, 外科口罩防嘅係飛沫粒子，即係我地用防毒面具代替，就要裝particulate filter，換言之，就係濾棉！<br />\n<br />\n濾棉最高級別就係P100，防油性+非油性粒子，即係TG（油性）同埋病毒都可以防，型號包括2091, 2097, 2297, 6035（只有英國製）,7093 等等，而60926等等嘅6092X 系列濾罐，因為內置P100 濾棉，所以一樣ok <br />\n其中，6053 同 7093 棉係防水的，清潔消毒會較方便，而60926表面亦有膠盒。<br />\n<br />\n有強國人做過測試，係北京霧霾毒氣之下，3M 2091 用左十一日過濾能力都係跌左1%，手足請自行考慮幾耐換一次。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon 大log買亦有便，大家可以組團買。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com.au%2F3M%2Fen_AU%2Fcompany-au%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B8711017%2B3294471754%26rt%3Drud&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=d946a461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com%2F3M%2Fen_US%2Fcompany-us%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B3294776429%26rt%3Drud&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=c6713ce8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<br />\n2003 年沙士，淘大嘅清理人員就係用2091棉+600X 罐（罐理論上唔洗，應該係防佢地嘅清潔同消毒藥水）。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">如何清潔防毒面具可參考依段片，有教disinfection，主要都係漂白水同消毒劑<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdE5IweYn3T4&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=44ac9a27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n清潔步驟：<br />\n入到屋企唔好除裝備住，用酒精紙巾抹左面具同濾棉/罐表面先，跟住抹埋手再洗手（點解又要酒精又要洗手係有原因的），跟住就除面罩，再跟番片入面嘅教學清潔<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n防毒面具方面，建議大家買/用6800 或者其他包曬成塊面嘅款式，咁樣就唔洗帶眼罩，一舊野保護曬成塊面，最安全。因為你戴半面+眼罩，咁就多舊野清潔，同埋部分眼罩封唔曬，冇咁安全。<br />\n<br />\n型號方面，全面嘅建議大家買6800，順便擋埋橡膠子彈，半面嘅就買7502/ 6500，兩款手足都表示舒適度幾高。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112044766987392%2Fposts%2F119490526242816%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=01346084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n</a><br />\n酒精搓手液 vs 洗手梘液</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/npptl/topics/respirators/factsheets/respsars.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fniosh%2Fnpptl%2Ftopics%2Frespirators%2Ffactsheets%2Frespsars.html&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=1824b02c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/npptl/topics/respirators/factsheets/respsars.html</a><br />\nSARS 時期CDC 對N95 同防毒面具嘅指引<br />\n（僅供參考！WARS 嘅傳染性係SARS 嘅一倍以上！！！！）"},{"pid":"6a29427742e2346720b24367210fe1e1bba9eda8","tid":1849842,"uid":143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:20:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39ca7e8fc940d07f108fb6bfec1760eb175bf0cb","tid":1849842,"uid":49992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:21:47.000Z","msg":"可能出街搵工"},{"pid":"1b85a3259386d882c4a33d2374ee2ef546d44657","tid":1849842,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"39ca7e8fc940d07f108fb6bfec1760eb175bf0cb","tid":1849842,"uid":49992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:21:47.000Z","msg":"可能出街搵工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:24:59.000Z","msg":"真心 你無口罩 屋企又唔係得你一個<br />\n你幾百蚊一盒都要買咖啦 無錢咪出聲<br />\n屈臣氏有得排又唔死去排<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有屋企人長期病患 條友係咪要咁撚自私先？<br />\n<br />\n個口罩用完又用 頭先又拎返嚟啦 <br />\n加下佢以為練蠱呀？救命 癡撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衰過唔帶"},{"pid":"092d0d43ace6f6b6063dea539d9f0b8a8b34b73c","tid":1849842,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a29427742e2346720b24367210fe1e1bba9eda8","tid":1849842,"uid":143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:20:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:25:31.000Z","msg":"聽日lock門"},{"pid":"6f88136c3ee9fe0fdd2b795010bb3f5897219b37","tid":1849842,"uid":6097,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"945ff8e05bd590ce04163642f19c6a2d54da9569","tid":1849842,"uid":233301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0d41add71f7f039886fa5d33ab3c55bd5739cc73","tid":1849842,"uid":6097,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"p